Name:                shady-graphics
Version:             0.6.1
Cabal-Version:       >= 1.6
Synopsis:            Functional GPU programming - graphics
Category:            Graphics
Description:
  Graphics types for Shady, for GPU execution
  See also shady-gen, shady-render, shady-tv, and shady-examples
  .
